text: "Krishan bhai, behna ko bura nhi laga"- Thats how it all started :P. The best gift jo eclub se mila. Thanks kaafi saare chocolates ke liye. Kabhi koi confusion ho, koi chinta ho, Monika always ready for expert advice. Ab shayad hyderabad jake rakhi bandhwana padega, saath m treat bhi lunga. Itne saare professors ko naam pata hota h tera, itne kaand jo kiye. 15 days DP change challenge toh shayad bas COVID m hi ho paaya tera, although ab back on track aa gayi. Not to mention chaapu to tu hai hi- Sports, padhai, fine arts, etc etc. Ab graduation khatam and "Tango charlie" back to work. Ab aaram se apna hindi sudhar lena ("Karunga, likhunga, padhunga"). Aage bohut jyada achieve karna "Jeevan m" :P. Stay happy always. All the best for your future. Best wishes

text:
Yo presi sir, apan k SoC k project epic the. Poora summer PUBG, phatta, baddy khelo and class jaate raho muh uthake. End m kuch kuch karke bana hi diya humne last days, jeetna toh kabhi tha nhi but maza bohut aaya uss fraud m. JD and aap hamare inspiration rehte the baddy m, but kabhi kabhi apna racquet bhi de diya karo :P. Kaafi suna h aapke politics ke paintre, uss politics ko salam. ECO221 m toh aapke doubts dekhke maine optional hi change kar diya (although yeh reason nhi tha :D). But jo bhi ho kaafi chaheete president ho gye aap hall 2 k. Aise hi achieve karte raho. All the best. 
Aur trend continue karne k liye #NotMyPresident
author: Soumya Ranjan Dash

text: Coordi banne se pehle toh kaafi kam baat hui hogi apni. But uske baad toh kaafi cheezen aligned hone lag gaya tha. Eclub wala tenure mazedar tha waise kaafi, khaas karke end m tere and jay k club renovation wale initiative. But sadly khud k liye club renovate karwaya humne and phir online hi graduate ho gaye. Fir aaya techmeet, uss time kaafi saare projects ek saath kar rhe the hum log. Kudos tujhe and Jay ko, saath m poori contingent ki management wale kaam bhi jo sambhal rahe the tumlog. Somewhere during this, pata chala ki tu gensec ka election ladega. I was like, "acha hai". But mera pehle se hi decided tha ki, election m bilkul nhi ghusna. And eventually pata nhi kaise, hall 4, hall 10, etc k bahar campaigning kar raha tha. Lastly, tere gensec tenure m, techmeet 9.0 ki jeet was most memorable on the whole journey. All the best for your future endeavours.
author: Soumya Ranjan Dash

text: Yo Naishadh!!!! Indeed a great guy with some serious ROS skills. Yahi impression tha there liye, during the early days in ERA. Later, got to see your management skills. Mulakat toh ERA se hi shuru hui thi apni. Learnt a lot from you, so thanks. Bas "Umbrella organisation" wala idea amar rahe :P. Kaafi diverse skills ka expert hai tu bro. author: Soumya Ranjan Dash

text:
A warm greeting to Nitish!!!! 
I feel privileged to have a friend like you who is so nice and dependable. It was a long journey sharing the experience of eclub secretary, eclub coordinator, team era, techmeets, TIIDC, etc with you.  I can easily remember you blushing to your praises :P. Those were some great times convincing you and eventually succeeding in getting parties from you. Sorry for being relatively poor in communicating in English besides you. 

Bas ab mujhse aur professional nahi bana jaega. Tum itna professional memoir likhte ho, dekhte inferiority complex feel hoti hai. Ab apne style m, tumhare saath ka journey bohut mazedaar tha. Tumse innocence m compete karna thoda muskil h. Chaapu researcher toh ban hi gaye ho tum. All the best for your future endeavors.
author: Soumya Ranjan Dash

text: Hi brother! 1st semester m mere liye sabse pehla and sabse dependable person tu tha. Kaafi similarity thi apni, same branch, same bapu, same PE bhi Lol. Yaad hai maine bhi drams join kiya tha, and wahan 10 din nhi tik paaya and tune toh wahan apna impression hi bana diya. Bhai jis dedication k saath tune drams kiya h, and then too time nikalke data science k field m itna excel kiya, kaafi kam k bas ki baat h yeh. Lots of wishes for you future ahead. Bohut excel karna life m.

text: Sandeep Bhai!!! I have known you from the JEE prep days in FIITJEE. Bohut hi jyada sincere and intelligent person. First of all mere JEE clear kr paane ka kaafi credit toh tere help ko jaata hai. But that was not it. College m bhi tune kaafi help kiya hai. Chahe exams k liye kuch last minute unsolvable doubts ho ya assignments ke koi doubts, you have cleared them all. Upar se apan toh 1st paper m bhi co-authors the. Kaafi kuch seekha h tere se. In any of my doubts, I was sure for one thing, agar end tak mujhe nahi samajh aaya then ask sandeep and you're done. Thanks for being so dependable. All the best for your future endevours. Stay in touch.
author: Soumya Ranjan Dash

text: 1st year guitar sessions toh kar liye apan ne but "sa re ga ma" me hi reh gaye :"). Room p movie screening, IPL m CSK ka blind support/ superstition overload, badminton ka nasha, life during the 1st (3 years to be precise) was interesting. Thank you for being the bestest (mujhe pata h aisa koi word exist nhi krta) friend(roomie P), to support in each and every troubles. All the best. Khoob saara achievements stack kro. Best wishes.

text:
""Acha chalta hoon
Duaaon mein yaad rakhna
Mere zikr ka zubaan pe swaad rakhna"".  
Gupta ji ka favourite gaana, waise ek hi toh gaana aata h and usme bhi bas yahi ek line :P Yeh zulfein har baar kyu saamne hi ferte ho, kya gam hai jisko chupa rahe ho. Aur phir tumhare gyani vichaar, "all are connected in this world" hamesha yaad rahega. Aise hi apne gyan se logon ko and Patel bhai k subscribers ko enlighten karte raho. Woh din door nhi jab "dogecoin" k badle "guddu_gupta_coin" market top kar rha hoga. Isi ke saath guddu gupta ji ko hamara pranam jataana. Kisi deepawali m apne ghar phirse bulana yaar and Vipul ko bulana mat bhoolna. On this note, best wishes. Apne life m khoob tarakki karna. "

text: I will start with, "Ab tum mere ghere m aa chuke ho". Uhhh! How to show that expressions of a tantric. Bhai jitna dhoka tune selmon bhai, Virat Kholi and (you know who) ko diya h utna dhoka toh maine bhi tumhe nhi diya hoga kabhi P. IPL wali fighting to forever yaad rahega, especially CSK vs SRH finals 2018. Bas iske baad kabhi ek season IPL dekhna h tere saath baithke and phir laddna h/chiddhana bhi h(Kyunki CSK jeetegi and DC haaregi P). Bas mujhe ek lecture dena, "how to control your anger", tere se best teacher nhi milega ab. From Civil to mech to CSE, bas kar pagle aur kitna door jaega. Waise hum ab alum ban jaenge and ..... D. Jokes apart, all the best for all your future success, and bohut jyada chaapna future m.
